high_descs: Turn left, move around the island to the right, head to the coffee machine on the left.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn left, bring the mug to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the mug in the coffee machine.
Take the heated mug back to the coffee machine, right of the sink.
Put the heated mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the sink, and find the coffee maker to the right of the sink.
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker.
Turn left, walk towards the stove, and find the microwave above the stove.
Heat up the cup and take it back out of the microwave.
Turn right and walk towards the coffee maker.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk through the kitchen to the coffee maker
Pick up the white mug from the coffee maker
Turn left and walk through the kitchen over to the microwave above the stove
Heat the mug in the microwave then remove it
Turn right and walk back around to the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the coffee maker
